  "remarks": "New People is a Russian political party. It supported Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine, and backed the illegal and unrecognised annexation of Ukraine’s Donetsk, Luhansk, Zaporizhzhia and Kherson regions by Russia. It also established a regional branch in the so-called “Donetsk People’s Republic”.",
